text: After all the time that has passed, after everything we have experienced, after everything we have done & achieved as a nation, these words still ring true. We have endured so much as a nation and we have prevailed. We will not be overwhelmed by uncertainty, fear or despondency.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: “It is true that we are facing a grave emergency. But if we act together, if we act now, and if we act decisively, we will overcome it.”
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: 15 months ago, as I addressed the nation from the Union Buildings, I said: “This epidemic will pass. But it is up to us to determine how long it will last, how damaging it will be, and how long it will take our economy and our country to recover.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
While it must be our unwavering determination to ensure that no health care workers are infected, this is a significant reduction in infections, which can be attributed to the success of the first phase of our vaccination programme.
 
This is evidence that vaccines work.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: In the last seven days, only 64 health care workers have been infected.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: As we see the rate of infection rise across the country, there is one statistic that provides a reason for hope. At a similar point in the rise of the 2nd wave of infections in early December last year, there were 640 health care workers infected by COVID-19 over a 7 day period.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: I call on everyone else, if you know someone over 60 years of age who has not been vaccinated, please help them to register and get vaccinated.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: I therefore call on every person in this country over the age of 60 to register – whether online, by SMS, by phone or in person – and get vaccinated without delay.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: It is estimated that we have the capacity at present to vaccinate at least 150,000 people a day, and we are planning to increase that to 250,000 a day as soon as possible.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: Now that the delays in the supply of vaccines is largely resolved, our immediate task is to complete the vaccination of all those over 60 years of age without delay.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: The initial doses we receive from Johnson & Johnson will be used to vaccinate educators in our schools and thereafter security personnel on the frontline.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: We have received an indication from Johnson & Johnson that it expects to deliver around 2 million vaccines to South Africa by the end of the month.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
The company has committed to significantly ramp up production and begin supplying the country within the next few days. We have to date received nearly 2.4 million Pfizer vaccine doses.
 
By the end of June, we expect to have received a total of 3.1 million Pfizer doses.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
The problems with the Johnson & Johnson vaccine have now been resolved. As a result of these problems, 2 million doses that had already been produced are unusable.
 
The Aspen plant in Gqeberha in the Eastern Cape is now able to go ahead and produce new doses.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
The pace of vaccinations has steadily picked up, and we are now vaccinating around 80,000 people a day at over 570 sites in the public and private sector.
 
This number will grow rapidly in the weeks to come, as we aim to protect as many vulnerable people as possible.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
As part of Phase Two, a further 1.5 million health workers and people over the age of 60 have received the first dose of the Pfizer vaccine.
 
This brings the total number of people who have received a vaccine dose to almost 2 million.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
Until now, our mass vaccination programme has therefore had to rely on the Pfizer vaccine, which requires two doses.
 
Nevertheless, 480,000 health workers have received the Johnson & Johnson vaccine to date as part of Phase One of the programme.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: However, the supply of Johnson & Johnson vaccines was held up by an investigation into contamination of ingredients at a supplier factory in Baltimore in the United States.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: After the AstraZeneca setback, the Johnson & Johnson vaccine appeared to be the best option for our country as it protects against the variant, because it requires only a single dose and is easier to store and transport.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
We each have a responsibility to take the necessary action to protect ourselves and others.
 
It is up to each one of us to limit the risk to ourselves and others.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
It remains mandatory for every person to wear a face mask that always covers their nose and mouth at all times when in public spaces.
 
It is a criminal offence not to do so.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: The owners and managers of public buildings, centres, shops, restaurants, taxis and buses all have a responsibility to ensure that people on their premises or in their vehicles wear masks. They must ensure that the appropriate social distancing measures are in place & adhered to.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: It is important to remember that it is a criminal offence if the number of people on these premises exceeds the maximum number of customers or employees allowed for there to be proper social distancing.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: This will now be a hybrid event, with a significantly reduced number of people physically in attendance, and a virtual address by the President.
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We all have a role in this great national effort to end "COVID19. Let us play our part. At this time, when the Easter message of hope, rebirth and renewal finds expression in the lives of so many of us, let us please take care." - President Ramaphosa #StaySafe https://t.co/3Am4CxHSMm
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Let us remain at home or in small groups. Let us avoid being in large crowds and places with poor ventilation. Let us not go to funerals unless we are immediate family and not visit the homes of the bereaved." - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/1kfSqx1jWR
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
"Fellow South Africans,
 
This pandemic is still very much with us.
 
We must act with caution, not just this coming weekend but in the days, weeks and months ahead." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 https://t.co/epIjcrPZyr
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We will review these measures on the size of gatherings within the next 15 days based on an assessment on the state of the pandemic and the extent of compliance with health protocols." - President Ramaphosa
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
"We continue to urge all SAns to avoid gatherings if they are in a vulnerable group, such as the elderly and those with co-morbidities.
 
We also urge that gatherings should take place in outdoor venues, which are significantly safer than gathering indoors." - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/KmBFaQtjXs
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Where the venue is too small to accommodate these numbers with appropriate social distancing, then no more than 50 per cent of the capacity of the venue may be used."- President Ramaphosa #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Following this consultation, it has been determined that religious gatherings over this period will be restricted to a total number of 250 people indoors and 500 outdoors." - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/fA7oBLW44Z
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "On-site sales at restaurants, shebeens and bars will be allowed, according to licensing conditions, up until 23:00." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 https://t.co/oNi6f6HQXP
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
"Given the role of #alcohol in fuelling reckless behaviour, we will put in place some restrictions over the Easter weekend.
 
To this end, the sale of alcohol for off-site consumption will be prohibited this coming Friday, Saturday, Sunday and Monday." - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/PC48lBrOfh
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Funerals remain restricted to a maximum of 100 people and with a two-hour limit on services. Interprovincial travel will still be permitted." - President Ramaphosa
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
"The #curfew is maintained from midnight to 4am.

However, this will continue to be subject to strict health protocols, such as social distancing, mask-wearing." - President Ramaphosa
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Given the relatively low transmission levels, we have decided to keep the country on coronavirus Alert #Level1. However, due to the specific circumstances of this period, we need to make a few adjustments." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe https://t.co/fDNYXcib1F
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Many of us have made plans for the upcoming long weekend. Some of us will be heading out of town; others will be visiting friends and family. Many of us will be attending gatherings and celebrations." - President Ramaphosa
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
"Fellow South Africans, In just a few days, the country will begin the annual Easter break.
 
For many, this will be a welcome moment to pause and rest, whether from work or from our studies, and from the pressures of the last months." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe https://t.co/pJgdvOqwuV
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "An Electronic Vaccination Data System has been established to manage the vaccine rollout and direct people towards vaccination sites closest to where they live." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Registration to be vaccinated is scheduled to start in April. People will be encouraged to register on-line, but those without on-line access will be able to register in person." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The 2nd phase of the #COVID19 vaccination programme aims to ensure that we will protect our communities, prevent health services from being overwhelmed & reduce the need for lockdowns that seriously disrupt education, the economy & each one of our lives." - President Ramaphosa
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The demand for vaccines around the world has become extremely competitive but we are doing our best to secure enough supply the people of South Africa and the African continent." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We are also in various stages of negotiations with the manufacturers of other vaccines such as Sinovac, Sinopharm and Sputnik V. Some of these manufacturers in the final stages of the approval process for use of the vaccines in SA." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We are also finalising an agreement for 20 million doses of the Pfizer vaccine, which requires two doses. Together, this supply of vaccines will provide us with enough doses to vaccinate 41 million people." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "More than 250,000 health workers have to date received the Johnson & Johnson vaccine as part of the Sisonke trial. We have secured 11 million doses of the Johnson & Johnson vaccine, which we know to be effective against the dominant variants in our country" - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/fzt5CUP0BB
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Our national vaccination programme has commenced and will be gaining momentum. In the middle of Feb, we began Phase 1 of our vaccination programme, which involves the vaccination of health workers. This phase is on track to be completed within three months" - President Ramaphosa https://t.co/8H36vXIWo3
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "It is also a testament to the high degree of vigilance we have continued to observe as a country with regards to monitoring, testing, contact tracing and preventive measures." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The number of hospitalisations is declining, as is the number of deaths. Our national recovery rate stands at slightly higher than 95%." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "As I reported when I last addressed you, SA has emerged from a second wave of infections. For the past two weeks, the number of new cases has remained relatively stable at around 1,200 new cases per day." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We miss the many things we once took for granted, like being able to visit our loved ones, go to a party, or attend religious services." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "What has perhaps been most difficult of all is how the pandemic has affected the social interactions that make us feel part of a community." - President Ramaphosa #COVID19 #StaySafe
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text:
Addressing corruption 

The Department of Justice and Constitutional Development is allocated R1.8 billion to improve business processes. This allocation will support our brave law
enforcement agents in the fight against crime and corruption.

text:
Public procurement and zero-based budgeting

Finalisation of the Public Procurement Bill is urgent. The National Treasury is fast tracking it. The bill addresses fragmentation in procurement legislation. We aim to table this reform before Cabinet before the end of this year

text:
Debt outlook

Our borrowing requirement will remain well above R500 billion each year of the medium term despite the modest improvements in our fiscal position. Consequently, gross loan debt will increase from R3.95 trillion in the current fiscal year to R5.2 trillion in 2023/24.

text:
Medium term spending plans and job creation

name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We all want to provide for our children, and we hope that they will enjoy better lives than we have had." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We share the same fears and anxieties about our future. We share the same hopes and desires." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate https://t.co/aAyAnsoCuJ
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "But I also spoke about our strength and resilience as a people. I spoke about the qualities that we share, and the common purpose that binds us together." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "I spoke about the pain and the sorrow and the hardship that so many have experienced and continue to experience." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "A week ago, I stood here to address the state of our nation. I was forthright about the severe challenges we face, about the many crises that we must endure and overcome." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "If we fail to see that potential, if we fail to recognise our strengths, then we will fail to seize the opportunities that they present for building a better society." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We are too often overcome by the unrelenting pressures of the moment, so that we fail to see the enormous potential that resides within this nation." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "I have spoken this afternoon of some of this country’s strengths and capabilities – of how we have nurtured them and how we continue to develop them – because all too often we overlook them."  #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The criticisms have contributed to getting us more focused, and the work being done in government has contributed toward us moving with speed." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We have entered a new era of implementation and action, of working with speed and urgency to follow through on our commitments." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Within only four months of its establishment in October last year, Operation Vulindlela has worked closely with and supported implementing departments to resolve obstacles to the implementation of crucial reforms." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "As several speakers in the debate noted, we do need to work with greater urgency to address the challenges that we face. That is why the State of the Nation Address focused on progress, not promises." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate https://t.co/hp3gUkle0e
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We are mindful that for our international tourism arrival numbers to reach pre-COVID levels, the vaccine rollout and adoption of bio-security standards remains critical." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We are working with the industry to promote renewed investment through a conducive policy and regulatory framework. This includes efforts to reduce current timeframes for mining, prospecting, water and environmental licences." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We have extensive reserves of some of the world’s most valuable minerals and extensive mining expertise. Mining was one of the sectors of our economy that recovered significantly following the easing of domestic and global lockdown restrictions." #SONA2021 #SONAReply
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The wealth that lies beneath our soil has been central to our country’s economy for nearly 150 years. However, this wealth has not been equally shared amongst the people of South Africa." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "South Africa is a country of great agricultural promise. We are a producer and exporter of a wide variety of agricultural products." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "The pandemic has also exposed the inequalities in access to healthcare and underscored the value of a national health insurance. While the pandemic has further constrained our public finances, in many ways it has also enabled progress towards the NHI." #SONA2021 #SONAReply
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Working with the private sector, state entities and development partners we have started training women entrepreneurs in financial literacy, accessing markets and access to finance." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate https://t.co/2vyBd1Z8eU
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "As government, we are working to give effect to our decision to direct at least 40 per cent of public procurement to women-owned business." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "We must support commercialisation of its products for domestic use and export, creating factories and manufacturing jobs." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Taken together, our national science and innovation system is a hugely valuable resource that we need to further nurture and develop." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate https://t.co/8EoEmlBKkT
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "Our vaccination programme, our best defence against this pandemic, has begun."  #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate https://t.co/9znmVGJbAi
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

text: "And so, before we get to the business of today, before we turn to our plans and to the immense work that lies ahead, let us give the courageous South African people the dues they so richly deserve." #SONA2021 #SONAReply #SONA2021Debate
name: South African Government
description: The official South African Government account, offering easy access to public information and services. Tel: 012 473 0000

name: South African Government
